message.content: It is difficult to make a generalization about all kids in Tunisia, as interests and obsessions can vary among individuals. However, like in many other countries, some common obsessions among kids in Tunisia may include technology, social media, video games, fashion trends, music, and celebrities. These are often influenced by global pop culture and trends. It is important to note that not all kids in Tunisia may have the same obsessions, as personal interests and preferences can differ.
